  "body": "### Description\n\nIt would be great if it was simpler to connect to DevServices from external sources. \r\nFor example, I'd love to be able to connect to a database started via devservices using an external client in order to troubleshoot.\r\n\r\n**Context**: I'd like to run an appliation in dev mode and from another terminal run a quarkus powered cli command to interact with that service. Currently, its a PITA to get the url, credentials etc.\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nThere are multiple ways we could go about it, but i I find really intersting the `workload projection` aka `kubernetes service binding directory structure`, as it enables the forementioned feature with the minimal dev and user effort.",
